      <title>日本对韩关系的看法自 2011 年以来最为积极</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/japanese-positive-views-of-south-korea-at-highest-since-2011</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在两国领导人努力建立更紧密关系的背景下，半数日本人认为日本与韩国关系良好，这是自 2011 年以来年度调查中的最高值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/japanese-positive-views-of-south-korea-at-highest-since-2011</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 03:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>四名美国大学教师在中国公园被刺伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/four-us-college-teachers-injured-in-china-park-stabbing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正值中国领导人习近平推动加强学术交流、增进两国关系之际，四名美国大学教师在中国一个公园被刺伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/four-us-college-teachers-injured-in-china-park-stabbing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国向越过边境的朝鲜军队发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/s-korea-fires-warning-shots-at-north-s-troops-crossing-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国军方称，周日数名朝鲜士兵短暂越过边境后，军方发出警告，此举可能进一步加剧半岛紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/s-korea-fires-warning-shots-at-north-s-troops-crossing-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:02:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯告诉士兵们要做好应对“更令人担忧”的威胁的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/marcos-tells-soldiers-to-prepare-for-more-worrisome-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯要求菲律宾北方部队做好应对中国和台湾之间紧张局势的任何准备，同时警告该国面临“更令人担忧”的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/marcos-tells-soldiers-to-prepare-for-more-worrisome-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 01:58:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉马杜罗准备签署协议承认选举结果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/venezuela-s-maduro-ready-to-sign-pact-to-recognize-vote-results-lx9ps6ei</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗愿意签署协议，承认下个月总统选举的结果，尽管民意调查仍然显示他落后于反对派鲜为人知的候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/venezuela-s-maduro-ready-to-sign-pact-to-recognize-vote-results-lx9ps6ei</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 01:19:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡加强对家族办公室和对冲基金的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/singapore-ramps-up-scrutiny-of-family-offices-hedge-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一系列丑闻凸显新加坡监管存在漏洞之后，新加坡当局要求家族办公室和对冲基金提供更多信息，同时加大对休眠公司的关闭力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/singapore-ramps-up-scrutiny-of-family-offices-hedge-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 00:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲁迪·朱利安尼在亚利桑那州遭遇假选举人团伙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-10/rudy-giuliani-processed-in-arizona-in-fake-electors-scheme-to-overturn-trump-s-2020-loss-to-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲尼克斯（美联社）——马里科帕县警长办公室称，纽约市前市长、唐纳德·特朗普的律师鲁迪·朱利安尼周一因试图推翻特朗普在亚利桑那州大选中输给乔·拜登的判决而受到刑事指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-10/rudy-giuliani-processed-in-arizona-in-fake-electors-scheme-to-overturn-trump-s-2020-loss-to-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 23:07:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将在 CEO 活动前与参议院共和党人会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/trump-to-meet-with-senate-republicans-before-ceo-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普将于周四会见参议院共和党人，这是华盛顿决策者为制定前总统赢得第二任期后的优先事项所做的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/trump-to-meet-with-senate-republicans-before-ceo-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 22:18:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>辞职法官警告香港法治面临“严重危险”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/top-hong-kong-court-loses-third-overseas-judge-as-scrutiny-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，一位从香港最高法院辞职的英国著名法官对中国打压异见人士的做法提出了严厉批评，警告称，香港这个金融中心的法治面临“严重危险”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/top-hong-kong-court-loses-third-overseas-judge-as-scrutiny-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 18:39:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与缓刑办公室的虚拟面试持续了 30 分钟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/trump-to-be-interviewed-by-probation-officers-in-hush-money-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普周一接受了纽约缓刑官的讯问，该缓刑官的量刑报告将帮助法官决定这位前总统因伪造商业记录将在监狱中服刑多长时间（如果有的话）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/trump-to-be-interviewed-by-probation-officers-in-hush-money-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 04:08:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
